        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel your <strong>courgette[s]</strong> into ribbons</p><p>Crumble your <strong>Greek cheese </strong>into rough bite-sized pieces</p><p>Strip your <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them finely, discard the stems</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2216-Step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2216-Step-5-x400.jpg",
