          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the juice of<strong> half</strong> your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> to a bowl with 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>water</strong></p><p>Add a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and stir it all together – this is your <strong>lemon dressing</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p><p>Wash your<strong> salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
